      "post_content": "About as good here as it was in Avacyn Restored. Meh. Put some flashback card in your graveyard in exchange for a new card, essentially trading half a card for a full one. Having haste is cool for a looter. But 4 is a little expensive, this deck wants its 4 drop to either do more or just be another 1-3 drop.",
