    {
      "id": "PopularPost307118",
      "post_content": "Curves with [rings of brighthearth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=rings of brighthearth) and works well with [Squee, Goblin Nabob](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Squee, Goblin Nabob). Overall compared to other colors' forms of filtering, this card is bad, but, in terms of what red can do in edh, these kinds of cards are nessecarry to have a deck with enough draw to fight through all the sweepers in the format. Cards like this are actually the nuts and bolts of a successful mono-red edh deck. In standard, this guys prolly not good enough, at 4 mana you should be playing something that's a problem for your opponent.",
      "posted_by": "Ligerman30",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost307118\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Curves with <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=rings of brighthearth\">rings of brighthearth</a> and works well with <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Squee, Goblin Nabob\">Squee, Goblin Nabob</a>.  Overall compared to other colors' forms of filtering, this card is bad, but, in terms of what red can do in edh, these kinds of cards are nessecarry to have a deck with enough draw to fight through all the sweepers in the format.  Cards like this are actually the nuts and bolts of a successful mono-red edh deck.  In standard, this guys prolly not good enough, at 4 mana you should be playing something that's a problem for your opponent.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy82380\">Ligerman30</span>\r\n                                (4/4/2013 2:21:28 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_pop