      "id": "PopularPost304966",
      "post_content": "this would have been prime real estate for an alternate art :P I would have actually liked this to have Blightning's art spot, but Blightning is the much splashier card.  \n  \nthe thing is, [Blightning](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blightning) doesn't NEED new art to make me play it. I love it already. :) This is admittedly a highly mechanically fitting card that just doesn't have enough Fire and Brimstone to feel Tibalt-y enough for me,   \n  \n.....and actually COULD have been given more Fire and Brimstone, and a [Tibalt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tibalt)-related flavor text even. :P Well, Wizards can't do EVERYTHING, and issues for common cards like this must be ranked pretty low on their to-do list compared to the ongoing debate in the Pit they MUST be having about 'When/How/Can/Do we reprint [Force of Will](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Force of Will) or [Jace, the Mind Sculptor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jace, the Mind Sculptor)?\"",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost304966\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">this would have been prime real estate for an alternate art :P I would have actually liked this to have Blightning's art spot, but Blightning is the much splashier card.<br/><br/>the thing is, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blightning\">Blightning</a> doesn't NEED new art to make me play it. I love it already. :) This is admittedly a highly mechanically fitting card that just doesn't have enough Fire and Brimstone to feel Tibalt-y enough for me, <br/><br/>.....and actually COULD have been given more Fire and Brimstone, and a <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tibalt\">Tibalt</a>-related flavor text even. :P Well, Wizards can't do EVERYTHING, and issues for common cards like this must be ranked pretty low on their to-do list compared to the ongoing debate in the Pit they MUST be having about 'When/How/Can/Do we reprint <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Force of Will\">Force of Will</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jace, the Mind Sculptor\">Jace, the Mind Sculptor</a>?\"</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46041\">DarthParallax</span>\r\n             